sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant WFCtrl as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC TLS1.2+
    participant S3 as S3/Minio Storage<br/>9000/443 HTTPS
    participant PersistAgent as Persistence Agent
    participant PodStep as Pipeline Step Pod

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via API

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Service Cert
    OAuth->>APIServer: HTTP Request<br/>Bearer Token
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Store pipeline definition<br/>MySQL Auth
    APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>Service Account
    APIServer-->>OAuth: Pipeline Created Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution (Workflow)

    K8sAPI->>WFCtrl: Watch Workflow CR created
    WFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pipeline Step Pod<br/>Service Account
    K8sAPI->>PodStep: Schedule Pod
    PodStep->>S3: Download artifacts<br/>S3 Credentials
    S3-->>PodStep: Artifacts
    PodStep->>MLMD: Record metadata<br/>mTLS (if podToPodTLS)
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Store lineage<br/>DB Credentials
    PodStep->>S3: Upload results<br/>S3 Credentials
    PodStep->>K8sAPI: Update Workflow status<br/>Service Account
    K8sAPI->>PersistAgent: Watch Workflow events
    PersistAgent->>MariaDB: Sync execution status<br/>DB Credentials

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Access

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/{id}<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    OAuth->>APIServer: HTTP Request<br/>Bearer Token
    APIServer->>S3: Generate signed URL (60s TTL)<br/>S3 Credentials
    S3-->>APIServer: Signed URL
    APIServer-->>OAuth: Redirect to signed URL
    OAuth-->>Route: Redirect Response
    Route-->>User: Signed URL (direct S3 access)

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: MLMD Metadata Query

    User->>Route: MLMD Query<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Route->>OAuth: Forward to MLMD Envoy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    OAuth->>MLMD: gRPC Request<br/>9090/TCP HTTP2
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Query metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    MariaDB-->>MLMD: Metadata results
    MLMD-->>OAuth: gRPC Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response
